name: Barbell
paragraph: A barbell is a piece of exercise equipment used in weight training, bodybuilding, weightlifting, powerlifting and strongman, consisting of a long bar, usually with weights attached at each end.

name: KetteleBell
paragraph: Kettlebells are great for building full-body strength, mobility, and even cardio endurance. The 'bells are a super-efficient way to work out, since each move works multiple muscle groups.

name: The chest fly machine
paragraph: The chest fly machine (also called pec fly machine) only targets one group of muscles the chest.
